em and are eliminated wherever Islam become dominant. Ignoring these inherent features is not tolerance it is willful blindness with severe consequences for liberty. Yes, be afraid of Islam, be very, very afraid.", "author": "SirGlornec", "created": 1784385221578, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "FraudFinder", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "FREE PEOPLE of the West and the world had better wake up and confront the reality of Islam before it\u2019s too late.", "last_comment_created": 1784386615018, "content": "<p>The Quran is not just a holy book to Muslims it is the literal, uncreated, eternal Word of God Himself: perfect, flawless, and final. No constitution, no human law, no other scripture can ever supersede it.</p>\n<p>Muhammad is the Seal of the Prophets and the complete, infallible role model for all time in religion, politics, warfare, family life, and personal conduct. His example and commands are binding forever. Sharia is not optional guidance. It is a complete, total, all-encompassing system designed to govern every aspect of individual, social, and political life under divine command. In traditional Islamic doctrine, implementing Sharia is a religious obligation.</p>\n<p>Orthodoxy enforcement runs deep in the faith. Deviation, criticism of core tenets, or leaving the religion are treated as serious communal threats worthy of death. In governments shaped by Islamic principles, Muslim leaders and officials are duty-bound to advance Sharia to the fullest extent possible. Failing to do is viewed as disobedience to God and blasphemy. This is not ancient history. These doctrines are foundational for all Muslims and actively are used to shape laws, societies, and political movements in country they occupy today.</p>\n<p>Western notions of secular pluralism, free speech, and freedom of conscience collide directly with this system and are eliminated wherever Islam become dominant. Ignoring these inherent features is not tolerance it is willful blindness with severe consequences for liberty. Yes, be afraid of Islam, be very, very afraid.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 2, "score_up": 42, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2078117724513837325", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ATBvLsk30", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 33, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8735362, "raw_content": "", "author": "bleeje", "created": 1784389739881, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Wexit-Delecto", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ATBvLsk30.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/avalon_tracy/status/2078117724513837325", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "\"My small town where a sunoco/convenience was bought recently by Indians, there's about 5-10 of them working  there, no Americans, they don't speak English, how? what special visa did they all use to get here & buy a business?\"", "last_comment_created": 1784393747128, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 12, "score_up": 33, "is_edited": false, "is_modera